{"id":"mibzar","term":"Mibzar","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Fortress, one of the Edomitish “dukes” descended from Esau (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 36:42\">Gen. 36:42</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 1:53\">1 Chr. 1:53</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Genesis 36:42","1 Chronicles 1:53"]}